  [Directions](https://www.undercanvas.com/camps/moab/#tab-7-1)
  
  **Directions from Salt Lake City, Utah**
  
  Take I-15 South for 47 miles. Merge onto US-6 for 150 miles. Take exit 182 towards Moab. Continue traveling south on Hwy 191, 18.9 miles or near mile marker 138. Turn east or left into Under Canvas Moab. If you pass the Chevron Station, you have gone too far. We are 0.6 miles south of Willow Springs Road.
  
  **Directions from Arches National Park (approx. 9-minute drive), Moab, Utah**
  
  Travel north on Hwy 191 towards Arches National Park Approximately 11 miles. Turn east or right into Moab Under Canvas. Our site is located between mile marker 137-138 at the first right turn after the Chevron Station or Arch View RV Resort. We are 0.6 miles north of 313 and .05 miles north of Arch View RV resort. \*\*Look for Lanterns & Solar Lights near Highway.
  
