  At Empty Spaces VRM, we are proud of providing premium luxury properties and delivering exceptional levels of service. Our managers, housekeepers, and maintenance teams are available 24/7 to answer questions and help with any hiccups during your stay. We have the best damage protection plan around so you can plan your vacation without worrying about the unpredictability of life. You are covered from liability for accidental damage to the property up to $1,500 with zero deductible!
  
